msgstr "Saat selesai, selalu panggil `finish_skill` jika tersedia.\n"

#: src/uagent/util_tools.py:793
msgid ""
"Select a skill number to run. Enter c to cancel.\n"
"Tip: :skills clear  (remove applied skills)\n"
"Enter number:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih nomor skill untuk dijalankan. Masukkan c untuk membatalkan.\n"
"Tip: :skills clear  (hapus skill yang diterapkan)\n"
"Masukkan nomor:"

#: src/uagent/util_tools.py:829
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Run this skill as a system-level instruction and keep it active in this session?\n"
"\n"
"Name: %(name)s\n"
"Path: %(path)s\n"
"\n"
"Proceed? Enter y to run, or c to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Jalankan skill ini sebagai instruksi tingkat sistem dan pertahankan aktif di sesi ini?\n"
"\n"
"Nama: %(name)s\n"
"Path: %(path)s\n"
"\n"
"Lanjutkan? Masukkan y untuk menjalankan, atau c untuk membatalkan."

#: src/uagent/util_tools.py:937
#, python-format
msgid ""
":clean will delete conversation log files (scheck_log_*.jsonl) from disk.\n"
"Log dir: %(dir)s\n"
"Rule: total user/assistant/tool messages excluding system <= %(threshold)d\n"
"Targets: %(n)d\n"
"\n"
"Proceed? Enter y to run, or c to cancel."
msgstr ""
":clean akan menghapus file log percakapan (scheck_log_*.jsonl) dari disk.\n"
"Direktori log: %(dir)s\n"
"Aturan: total pesan user/assistant/tool tanpa system <= %(threshold)d\n"
"Target: %(n)d\n"
"\n"
"Lanjutkan? Masukkan y untuk menjalankan, atau c untuk membatalkan."

#: src/uagent/util_tools.py:1181
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Delete {count} path(s)?\n"
"\n"
"{paths}\n"
"\n"
"Enter y to proceed, or c to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Hapus {count} path?\n"
"\n"
"{paths}\n"
"\n"
"Masukkan y untuk melanjutkan, atau c untuk membatalkan."

